The paper discusses issues related to data privacy, ownership, and exchange in the context of machine learning, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed solution involves a new paradigm for model training using blockchain technology, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG), distributed computing (cs.DC), data structures (cs.DS), and databases (cs.DB).
